quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  16,55,"Khobakhaye ebiakhwabahelesia. Kho, mwikhoye. Mulitsa okhumanya."
  16,56,"Ne ebuleka webindu biakhubakabile babishilanga balia kata balamanyile tawe. Toto mulirebwa kalia koosi akamwachikhanga."
  16,57,"Ne barererangao Nyasaye Abana abakhana. Nyasaye ni Omutswenufu ehale nende ako, nabo beyenyelanga ababachama."
  16,58,"Ne mulala wabu naboolelwa amakhuwa kokhwibula omwana omukhana, obweni bwaye bumaliyanga ne yetsula nende eshibeela."
  16,59,"Yefisa mubandu khulwokhubolelwa amakhuwa amabii kabolelwe. Yereba mbu: 'Amenye ninaye nende tsisoni nohomba amuyabile mwiloba?' Manya mbu ni obubii muno obo obwababusinjia."
  16,60,"Ne balia balasuubilanga mwikulu tawe, bali nende ifwani imbii, naye Nyasaye niye weyifuma yoluyali muno, naye niwa Amaani, Owamachesi muno."
  16,61,"Ne Nyasaye abukulilanga Abandu obubii khububii bwabu, shiyakhaleshelekhwo isolo yosiyosi khushialo tawe. Halali ababikhanga okhula ebise biarebwaho. Ne ebise biabu nibiliula, shibalishinda isandala tawe nohomba shibaliiyungubasia tawe."
  16,62,"Ne bahelesinjia Nyasaye ebindu biabasinya, ne tsinimi tsiabu tsiboolanga obubeyi mbu bo balanyoola amalayi. Toto abo babishilwa omulilo, ne toto balilekhwamwo."
  16,63,"Nditsuba khu Nyasaye mbu toto efwe khwaruma (Abarumwa) mumikanda chiaranjilila imbeli wuwo, halali Shetani yabaronela ebikhole biabu. Kho, olwalelo ye niye omwitsa wabu. Nabo bali nende eshinyasio eshilulu."
  16,64,"Ne shikhwakhwishilia Eshitabu halali obenosilie kalia akabakabukhanangamwo, ne shibe obulunjifu nende tsimbabaasi khubandu basuubilanga."